    <title>1837 Nov. 20, Carthage, Tennessee [to unknown recipient] / Adam Fergusson</title>
  </titleInfo>
  <abstract>This is a letter from Adam Fergusson dated November 20, 1837. The recipient is unknown, but is from Scotland. Fergusson is writing because he wishes information from his parents hometown in Scotland. He gives the names of his relations there, and where they are from. Fergusson requests that the recipient find someone willing to correspond with him.</abstract>
